# Design System – Dark & Light Mode Theming

**Figma reference:** [Light/Dark Mode Setup](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=522-12151&p=f&m=dev)

Decision rules below are derived from Figma node 522:12151. Use **only** tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc`; never hardcode hex values in components.

---

## When to switch

- **Light mode:** Default. Use when `data-theme="light"` or no attribute on `<html>`.
- **Dark mode:** Use when `data-theme="dark"` on `<html>`.

Layout and component structure stay identical; only token values change.

---

## Decision Rules – When to Use What Color

### 1. Backgrounds (surfaces)

| Use case | Light | Dark | Token |
|----------|-------|------|-------|
| Main page / app background | `#ffffff` | `#0c1723` | Bg/Default/Default (light) / Secondary (dark) |
| Secondary / negative space | `#f3f4f4` | `#0c1723` | Bg/Default/Secondary |
| Cards, panels, modals | `#ffffff` | `#202a35` | Bg/Default/Default |
| Tertiary surfaces (dividers, sections) | `#e8e9ea` | `#19242f` | Bg/Default/Tertiary |
| Input / select fields | `#ffffff` | Darker than page background | Bg/Default/Default (inputs) |
| Disabled surfaces | `#dee1e2` | `#38414b` | Bg/Disabled/Default |

**AI rule:** Use `--bg-base-default` for primary surfaces (cards, modals, panels). Use `--bg-base-secondary` for page background. Use `--bg-base-tertiary` for tertiary surfaces.

---

### 2. Text

| Use case | Light | Dark | Token |
|----------|-------|------|-------|
| Primary text (headings, body) | `#0c1723` | `#f6f7f7` | Text/Base/Default |
| Secondary text (labels, captions) | `#39414c` | `#cfd2d4` | Text/Base/Secondary |
| Tertiary / muted | `#565d66` | `#a8acb0` | Text/Base/Tertiary |
| Placeholder | `#bbbfc2` | Lighter gray | Text/Disabled/Placeholder |
| Disabled | `#9ea3a8` | `#9ea3a8` | Text/Disabled/Default |
| On brand CTA (buttons) | `#f6f7f7` | `#0c1723` | Text/Brand/On Brand |

**AI rule:** Always use `--text-base-default` / `--text-base-secondary` / `--text-disabled-default`; never hardcode.

---

### 3. Brand / Primary CTA

| Use case | Light | Dark | Token |
|----------|-------|------|-------|
| Primary button | `#008280` | `#00d0cd` | Bg/Brand/Default |
| Primary button hover | `#027575` | `#3edad8` | Bg/Brand/Hover |
| Text on brand | `#f6f7f7` | `#0c1723` | Text/Brand/On Brand |
| Brand secondary (tint) | `rgba(0,130,128,0.12)` | `rgba(0,208,205,0.16)` | Bg/Brand/Tertiary |
| Selected / active state | `rgba(0,130,128,0.40)` | `rgba(0,208,205,0.56)` | Bg/Brand/Secondary |

**AI rule:** Primary brand stays teal. Light mode: darker teal; dark mode: brighter teal for contrast. Use `--bg-brand-default` / `--text-brand-default` / `--border-brand-default` via CSS variables.

---

### 4. Secondary / Ghost buttons

| Use case | Light | Dark | Token |
|----------|-------|------|-------|
| Background | `#ffffff` | Darker than page | Bg/Default/Default |
| Border | `#dee1e2` | `#38414b` | Border/Base/Default |
| Text | `#0c1723` | `#f6f7f7` | Text/Base/Default |
| Hover | `rgba(0,130,128,0.08)` | `rgba(0,208,205,0.16)` | Bg/Default/Default Hover |

**AI rule:** Secondary buttons: `--bg-base-default` surface with `--border-base-default` + `--text-base-default`; no brand fill.

---

### 5. Borders

| Use case | Light | Dark | Token |
|----------|-------|------|-------|
| Default borders | `#dee1e2` | `#38414b` | Border/Base/Default |
| Secondary / dividers | `#bbbfc2` | `#646b72` | Border/Base/Secondary |
| Tertiary / subtle | `#81878d` | — | Border/Base/Tertiary |
| Brand focus | `#008280` | `#00d0cd` | Border/Brand/Default |

**AI rule:** Use `--border-base-default` or equivalent for borders; never hardcode.

---

### 6. Alerts / Notifications

| Semantic | Container | Icon/Text | Button |
|----------|-----------|-----------|--------|
| Danger / error | `--bg-danger-tertiary` | `--text-danger-default` | `--bg-danger-default` bg, `--text-brand-on-brand` text |
| Warning | `--bg-warning-tertiary` | `--text-warning-default` | `--bg-warning-default` bg, `--text-base-default` text |
| Success | `--bg-success-tertiary` | `--text-success-default` | `--bg-success-default` bg, `--text-brand-on-brand` text |
| Info | `--bg-brand-tertiary` | `--text-brand-default` | `--bg-brand-default` bg, `--text-brand-on-brand` text |

**AI rule:** Use semantic tokens above. Text on filled buttons: `--text-brand-on-brand` for dark fills (danger, success, brand).

---

### 7. Tags / Chips

| Use case | Light | Dark | Token |
|----------|-------|------|-------|
| Background | `#ffffff` or `#f3f4f4` | `#19242f` | Bg/Default/Tertiary |
| Border | `#dee1e2` | `#38414b` | Border/Base/Default |
| Text | `#0c1723` | `#f6f7f7` | Text/Base/Default |
| Remove icon | `--text-danger-default` for destructive; `--text-brand-default` for non-destructive |

**AI rule:** Tags use `--bg-base-tertiary`; semantic variants use `--bg-success-tertiary`, `--bg-warning-tertiary`, `--bg-danger-tertiary` with matching text tokens.

---

### 8. Inputs

| Use case | Light | Dark | Token |
|----------|-------|------|-------|
| Background | `#ffffff` | Slightly lighter than page | Bg/Default/Default |
| Border | `#dee1e2` | `#38414b` | Border/Base/Default |
| Text | `#0c1723` | `#f6f7f7` | Text/Base/Default |
| Placeholder | `#bbbfc2` | `#a8acb0` | Text/Disabled/Placeholder |
| Focus border | `#008280` | `#00d0cd` | Border/Brand/Default |

**AI rule:** Inputs use `--bg-base-default`; borders use `--border-base-default`; focus uses `--border-brand-default`.

---

### 9. Icons

| Use case | Light | Dark | Token |
|----------|-------|------|-------|
| Default | `#0c1723` | `#f6f7f7` | Icon/Base/Default |
| Secondary | `#39414c` | `#cfd2d4` | Icon/Base/Secondary |
| Tertiary | `#565d66` | `#a8acb0` | Icon/Base/Tertiary |
| On brand | `#f6f7f7` | `#0c1723` | Icon/Brand/On Brand |

**AI rule:** Match icon color to text hierarchy; use `--text-base-default`, `--text-base-secondary`, `--text-brand-default`, `--text-brand-on-brand`.

---

### 10. Modals / Overlays

| Use case | Light | Dark | Token |
|----------|-------|------|-------|
| Modal background | `#ffffff` | `#202a35` | Bg/Default/Default |
| Backdrop | `rgba(0,0,0,0.70)` | `--bg-blanket` |
| Scrim | Light: `rgba(255,255,255,0.80)`; Dark: `rgba(0,0,0,0.80)` | `--bg-scrim` |

**AI rule:** Modal content uses `--bg-base-default`; backdrop always same dark overlay.

---

## AI Guidelines – Summary

1. **Never hardcode colors.** Use `var(--token-name)` or Tailwind arbitrary values.
2. **Theme via `data-theme`** on `<html>`. Tokens switch automatically.
3. **Primary brand:** Teal in both modes; darker in light, brighter in dark.
4. **Structure:** Layout and hierarchy identical; only colors change.
5. **Semantic colors:** Use `--bg-danger-default`, `--bg-warning-default`, `--bg-success-default` and their tertiary/text variants per design-system-tokens.mdc.
6. **Color primitives:** Gray and Teal scales map to semantic tokens. Use semantic tokens only; see `design-system-tokens.mdc`.
7. **Hover states:** Use Bg/Default/Default Hover or Bg/Brand/Hover per context.
8. **Missing token:** Request it; do not invent.

---

## Quick Reference – CSS Variable Mapping

| Semantic | CSS var |
|----------|---------|
| Primary surface | `--bg-base-default` |
| Page background | `--bg-base-secondary` |
| Tertiary surface | `--bg-base-tertiary` |
| Border | `--border-base-default` |
| Primary CTA (fill) | `--bg-brand-default` |
| Primary CTA (text) | `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Brand tertiary (selected/hover) | `--bg-brand-tertiary` |
| Primary text | `--text-base-default` |
| Secondary text | `--text-base-secondary` |
| Disabled text | `--text-disabled-default` |
